    "A higher specificity means that the algorithm is better at correctly identifying normal instances as normal.",
    "This is important to avoid unnecessary alerts for normal operations.Figure 9 provides the comparison of false alarm rate.",
    "The false alarm rate is crucial in assessing the accuracy of anomaly detection systems in WSNs.",
